ratio in patients with bone metastases.

Thio QCBS(1), Goudriaan WA(2), Janssen SJ(3), Paulino Pereira NR(2), Sciubba 
DM(4), Rosovksy RP(5), Schwab JH(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Orthopaedics, Division of Orthopaedic Oncology, Massachusetts 
